Package dao

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CreateRecipeDao
    Create the recipe in the DB.
    DetailedRecipeDao
    This interface is used to get the detailed Recipe(ingredients)
    LoginDao
    This is used to check whether the user account is existed.
    RegisterDao
    This is used to add an account in the DB.
    SaveRecipeDao
    This class is used to save the recipe to the DB
    SearchRecipeDao
    This is used to search the recipe from the DB.
    ShowRecipeDao
    To show the details of a recipe from the DB.
    StarDao
    Star and unstar the recipe with a specified user.
